### Remaining Concerns
- The diagnosis section opens on `The collapses are what settle it` — plural, when the reader has seen one collapse teased and not yet described. It reads as a forward promise the piece does keep, so I left it. Worth noting that the fingerprint ledger records this opener as deliberately rewritten off the house stem to clear the same-type similarity scan, so rewording it would need a re-run of `scripts/same-type-similarity.mjs`.
- The dance-class payoff promised in the cold open lands five sections later. Each intervening section builds the measurement frame and two of them are dance nodes, so the deferral is earned, but it is the longest open loop in the piece. Your call whether it needs an earlier anchor.
